name: 可可·泰勒
introduction: Coco Taylor is a London-based British actor with recent film credits in horror, comedy and drama - roles in 2023/24 include three heroines, a killer, a vampire and a schoolgirl bully. She was accepted for the National Youth Theatre in 2023. Outside of acting Coco has a First Class Honours degree from the University of Bristol and sporting experience in equestrian (British Eventing 2* level/GB U16 squad) and skiing (gold medals at British Schoolgirls' Races in Slalom and Giant Slalom).
